3 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1181,\u00a0S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 92 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3239,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/05\/19\/isa-abd-allah-ruh-maryam\/","url_meta":{"origin":1420,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Eisa: Whoever testifies that Jesus is the servant of Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 19, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"'Ubadah ibn al-Samit reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever testifies that there is no God but Allah alone without any partners, that Muhammad is His servant and His Messenger, that Jesus is the servant of Allah and His Messenger, His word which He\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2016,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/02\/28\/hereafter-faith-eventually-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":1420,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Akhirah: Whoever has faith eventually enters Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 28, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Dharr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cGabriel, upon him be peace, came to me to give the good news that anyone from my nation who dies without associating partners with Allah will eventually enter Paradise.\u201d I said, \u201cEven if he commits adultery\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Fai